routine.title: G Major Two Note Scale Pattern
routine.description:
Hold the note for the full value. 
Use a comfortable dynamic. 
Strive for a consistent, clear, in-tune, sound.

routine.title: G Major Quarter Note One Note Rhythm
routine.description:
Hold the note for the full value. 
Use a comfortable dynamic. 
Repeat twice and end with a good whole note.
Play well 5 times.

routine.title: G Major Dotted Half Note Long Tone
routine.description:
Hold the note for the full value, off on 1 (-1). 
Use a mp to mf dynamic. 
Strive for a consistent, clear, in-tune, sound.

routine.title: G Major Quarter Note One Note Rhythm
routine.description:
Hold each note for the full value. 
Use a comfortable dynamic. 
Repeat twice and end with a good whole note.
Play well 5 times.
